      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a budget-friendly ride that's ready to hit the road! This car is a solid choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a great value. It shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, including some visible cosmetic blemishes and minor mechanical needs, but it's still a dependable worker. Perfect for a daily commuter looking for a practical deal!",
