    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows signs of regular use over the years. The exterior paint has several noticeable scratches and a few small door dings, along with some clear coat peeling on the rear bumper. The interior is generally clean but does show wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car is functional and starts reliably, though the air conditioning is not as cold as it once was and the tires will likely need replacement within the next few months. It serves as a dependable point-A-to-point-B vehicle but would benefit from some cosmetic and mechanical attention to bring it back to its best.",
      "price": 19500.0,
